										<li id="comment-52180" class="commentbody"><div class="commenthead"><img alt='Lotus`s avatar' src='http://trilema.com/2011/ce-vindem-ce-cumparam/avatar.png' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />								<div class="commentcount">6</div>
								<span class="authorlink"><a href='http://trilema.com/2011/ce-vindem-ce-cumparam/#comment-57409' class='url'>Lotus</a></span>&nbsp;								<span class=""></span>
