										<li id="comment-52209" class="commentbody"><div class="commenthead"><img alt='Dr.A`s avatar' src='http://blog.adrian.mihalcioiu.ro/2011/stiri-pe-care-nu-le-citeste-nimeni.html/avatar.png' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />								<div class="commentcount">15</div>
